# =============================================================================
# Storage/App/Public Directory - .gitignore
# =============================================================================
# This directory stores publicly accessible files like uploaded images,
# documents that users can access via the web.
# These files should not be in version control as they are user-generated.
# =============================================================================

# Ignore all files (user uploads, generated files, etc.)
*

# Keep .gitignore so the directory structure is preserved
!.gitignore
